body: It is a good product for storage of all your documents  Pro - 1- Good product to organize important documents and letters 2- Many divisions that can be easily marked using the strips that comes with the product. 3- Looks good from the outside too.  Con -  1- I'm concerned with the clasp. It looks fragile and easily breakable.  Over all - It is a good product and worth for the price you are getting it.  Recommendation - I recommend it as a must for document storage.
